HEADWORD: Hysterogenic
<hw>Hys`ter*o*gen"ic</hw> <pr>(?)</pr>, <pos>a.</pos>
<ety>[<ets>Hyste</ets>ria + root of Gr. <grk>gi`gnesqai</grk> to be
born.]</ety> <fld>(Physiol.)</fld> <def>Producing hysteria; <as>as, the
<ex>hysterogenic</ex>pressure points on the surface of the body,
